title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Forever Uncut TMNT
description:
Originally uploaded by XxSargeSlapAHoexX, 

so I take no credit for this release but 

I'm sure this is not the original title.

This version was only aired on American TV 

twice, and only released uncut in PAL 

territories.  It contains an additional 8 

minutes of footage from the later TV edit 

(and subsequent US DVD release).

Length 01:20:45
Resolution: 720x480
Data rate: 588kbps
Total bitrate: 714kbps
Frame rate: 29fps

Audio bitrate: 125 kbps, stereo 44kHz

from IMDB:
"The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles meet 

their match -- Literally! The modern, 

gritty Ninja Turtles must team up with 

their classic cartoon counterparts to stop 

two Shredders and their plans of multi-

dimensional scale."

This is a must-watch for any TMNT fan, 

regardless of what iteration(s) you are 

familiar with.

Please seed to help a newbie out!
